strings:
<voice_0x01000D16><se_low>King Trode: Medea! Where's Medea!?
She's gone!
<voice_0x01000D18><se_low>Yangus: People round 'ere don't care where ya come FROM, they care about wot ya come WIV!
<voice_0x01000D19><se_low>King Trode: Are you saying some ninny-hammer crook from this slum has kidnapped my daughter!?

<voice_0x01000D1A><se_low>Yangus: Oh, keep yer 'air on, Grandad!
Whoever it was can't o' gone far...
They'll still be in town somewhere.

<voice_0x01000D1B><se_low>King Trode: Well we must find them then!
Forget everything else!
Getting Medea back is all that matters!

<voice_0x01000D1C><se_low>King Trode: Well what are you waiting for, <hero>!? You heard me didn't you!?
We must find the culprit immediately and
save my precious daughter!
